OL,3,C'What would the world be like without
OL,4,Ca war?': Vivid memories of VE Day
OL,6,FMany of those who can remember Victory
OL,7,Fin Europe Day were children at the
OL,8,Ftime. The war had taken a large chunk
OL,9,Fof their childhoods, and they knew
OL,10,Flittle else.
OL,12,FJoan Herring and Mary Beresford were
OL,13,Fin their early teens on VE Day. They
OL,14,Fboth now live in a care home in Quorn,
OL,15,Fin Leicestershire, but can vividly
OL,16,Frecall where they were, and what they
OL,17,Fwere doing, when the war finally ended.
