OL,3,C'What would the world be like without
OL,4,Ca war?': Vivid memories of VE Day
OL,6,FJoan was 15 and on her way to get her
OL,7,Fphotograph taken in a studio with a
OL,8,Ffriend when news broke that the war
OL,9,Fhad ended.
OL,11,FShe said: "We got off the bus to go
OL,12,Fand have out photograph taken and
OL,13,Fpeople were going mad. They were
OL,14,Frunning in and out of shops, shouting
OL,15,Fand just standing there and shouting.
OL,17,F"We were absolutely amazed. I hadn't
OL,18,Fregistered at all that it was going to
OL,19,Fstop. So we just progressed and had
OL,20,Four photographs taken and went home.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
