OL,3,C'What would the world be like without
OL,4,Ca war?': Vivid memories of VE Day
OL,6,FJoan and her parents joined the
OL,7,Fthousands of revellers in the centre
OL,8,Fof London.
OL,10,FShe said: "We went up the Mall to
OL,11,FBuckingham Palace and just watched
OL,12,Fpeople for a long while.
OL,14,F"There were people up lampposts, there
OL,15,Fwere people up trees. There were
OL,16,Fpeople dancing, there was congas,
OL,17,Fdozens of congas going on, and
OL,18,Feverybody was singing and everybody
OL,19,Fseemed to be in uniform.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
