OL,3,C'What would the world be like without
OL,4,Ca war?': Vivid memories of VE Day
OL,6,FMary said: "We were amazed about the
OL,7,Fnumber of people who were there and we
OL,8,Fgot in, people behind us, people at
OL,9,Fthe side, people on the other side,
OL,10,Fmore people behind us, more people on
OL,11,Feach side, people in front.
OL,13,F"Then all of a sudden we were in this
OL,14,Fgreat crowd and I was quite
OL,15,Foverwhelmed and frightened. So that in
OL,16,Fa way was my reaction, rather than
OL,17,Fhappiness.
