OL,3,C'What would the world be like without
OL,4,Ca war?': Vivid memories of VE Day
OL,6,F"Everybody was singing, shouting,
OL,7,Fwaving anything they had to hand. It
OL,8,Fcould have been a scarf, it could have
OL,9,Fbeen a sock. We didn't have so many
OL,10,Fthings like flags in those days."
OL,12,FJoan and Marys childhood's were
OL,13,Fdefined by the war, peace seemed like
OL,14,Fan unknown quantity.
OL,16,FJoan said: "I remember thinking to
OL,17,Fmyself there's no war anymore, what's
OL,18,Fit going to be like? What is it to
OL,19,Flive in a land where there isn't any
OL,20,Fwar?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/8
